nnoremap <silent> [unite]gb :<C-u>Unite giti/branch<CR>
nnoremap <silent> [unite]gB :<C-u>Unite giti/branch_all<CR>
nnoremap <silent> [unite]gc :<C-u>Unite giti/config<CR>
